<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Certificate Under Review - Dealo</title>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: "Segoe UI", sans-serif;
        background-color: #ecfdf5;
        padding: 40px;
        color: #1e3a2d;
        margin: 0;
      }
      .container {
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: auto;
        background: white;
        border-radius: 12px;
        overflow: hidden;
        box-shadow: 0px 5px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      }
      .header {
        background-color: #047857;
        padding: 24px;
        text-align: center;
      }
      .header img {
        max-width: 140px;
      }
      .content {
        padding: 30px;
        text-align: center;
      }
      h2 {
        color: #065f46;
        font-size: 22px;
        margin-bottom: 16px;
      }
      p {
        color: #064e3b;
        font-size: 16px;
        line-height: 1.6;
      }
      .footer {
        background-color: #f0fdf4;
        padding: 20px;
        text-align: center;
        font-size: 13px;
        color: #64748b;
      }
      .footer a {
        color: #065f46;
        text-decoration: none;
      }
      .footer a:hover {
        text-decoration: underline;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <!-- Header -->
      <div class="header">
        <img
          src="https://pub-734ce1bac5434727ba9692dacb3d7441.r2.dev/logos/dealo-new.png"
          alt="Dealo Logo"
        />
      </div>

      <!-- Content -->
      <div class="content">
        <h2>Hi <%= firstName %>,</h2>
        <p>
          Thank you for uploading your certificate. Our team is currently
          reviewing your submission to verify its authenticity.
        </p>
        <p>
          This process usually takes between
          <strong>2 to 5 business days</strong>. Once approved, your profile
          will display a verified badge.
        </p>
        <p>
          You’ll receive another email as soon as we complete the review. If you
          have any questions, feel free to contact us at
          <a href="mailto:support@dealo.com">support@dealo.com</a>.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Footer -->
      <div class="footer">
        <p>
          <strong>Dealo Talent Network</strong><br />
          23A, Bashorun Okusanya Street,<br />
          Off Admiralty Road, Off Admiralty Way,<br />
          Lekki Phase 1, Lagos<br />
          <a href="mailto:support@dealo.com">support@dealo.com</a>
        </p>
        <p>© 2025 Dealo Talent Network. All rights reserved.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
